    "type": "message",
    "text": "I'm thinking about some sort of \"journal\" attached to a \"federated conference\" sort of thing! I really love how <https://hackclub.com|Hack Club> runs their clubs, where they provide toolkits and software and resources for local groups to run a club, and i feel a fedi-conf could do something like that, with presentations running online, and a sort of local \"hallway track\"",
